<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٩٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يَرْجِعُونَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> إِلَى الدُّنْيَا؛ لِيَسْتَدْرِكُوا مَا فَرَّطُوا فِيهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٩٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُتِحَتْ يَاجُوجُ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> سَدُّ يَاجُوجَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٩٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَدَبٍ}</span> ... مُرْتَفِعٍ مِنَ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٩٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَنسِلُونَ}</span> ... يُسْرِعُونَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٩٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْوَعْدُ الْحَقُّ}</span> ... يَوْمُ القِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٩٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَاخِصَةٌ}</span> ... مَفْتُوحَةٌ لَا تَكَادُ تَطْرِفُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٩٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَصَبُ جَهَنَّمَ}</span> ... وَقُودُهَا، وَحَطَبُهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَارِدُونَ}</span> ... دَاخِلُونَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَفِيرٌ}</span> ... تَنَفُّسٌ شَدِيدٌ تَنْتَفِخُ مِنْهُ الضُّلُوعُ يَدُلُّ عَلَى شِدَّةِ عَذَابِهِمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَسِيسَهَا}</span> ... صَوْتَ لَهِيبِهَا، وَاحْتِرَاقِ الأَجْسَادِ فِيهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْفَزَعُ الْأَكْبَرُ}</span> ... الهَوْلُ الأَعْظَمُ يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَطَيِّ السِّجِلِّ لِلْكُتُبِ}</span> ... كَمَا تُطْوَى الصَّحِيفَةُ عَلَى مَا كُتِبَ فِيهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الزَّبُورِ}</span> ... الكُتُبِ المُنَزَّلَةِ عَلَى الأَنْبِياءِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الذِّكْرِ}</span> ... اللَّوْحِ المَحْفُوظِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آذَنتُكُمْ}</span> ... أَعْلَمْتُكُمْ مَا أُمِرْتُ بِهِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَى سَوَاءٍ}</span> ... أَنَا وَأَنْتُمْ مُسْتَوُونَ فِي العِلْمِ بِهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>